text: Yuri Kazama (born 3 October 1996) is a Japanese water polo player. She was part of the Japanese women's national water polo team at the 2015 World Aquatics Championships and 2019 Summer Universiade. == References == == Other websites == * water-polo-th-fina-world-championships-day-six * yuri-kazama- jpn-water-polo * yuri-kazama Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Japanese water polo players
